Label the centre of the square grid as (0,0), the positive x-axis to the right and the positive y-axis upward.

In the Ulam (counter-clockwise) spiral

• every point (x , y) lies in the ring  
  k = max(|x| , |y|) (side-length 2k+1);

• the greatest number in that ring,  
  maxVal = (2k+1)², is found at the bottom-right corner (k , –k);

• going round the ring counter-clockwise the numbers decrease.
  Hence, for a given side the “distance’’ (offset) from maxVal is:

 bottom row (y = –k): offset = k – x  
 left   side (x = –k): offset = 2k + (y + k)  
 top    row (y =  k): offset = 4k + (x + k)  
 right  side (x =  k, y ≠ –k): offset = 6k + (k – y)

and the value at (x , y) is N(x , y) = maxVal – offset.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
1.  Locate 2026  

2025 = 45² is at (22, –22) (bottom-right of ring 22).  
2026 is one step to the right, i.e. at (23, –22).  
So 2026 is the first point of ring 23.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
2.  The 8 neighbouring coordinates of (23, –22)

SW  (22, –23)  S  (23, –23)  SE (24, –23)  
 W  (22, –22)         E  (24, –22)  
NW  (22, –21)  N  (23, –21)  NE (24, –21)

--------------------------------------------------------------------
3.  Calculate each neighbour

• Ring 23 (k = 23, maxVal = 47² = 2209)

  (22, –23): bottom row offset = 23 – 22 = 1 → 2209 – 1 = 2208  
  (23, –23): bottom-right            → 2209  
  (23, –21): right side offset = 6·23 + (23 – (–21)) = 138 + 44 = 182  
                        → 2209 – 182 = 2027  

• Ring 24 (k = 24, maxVal = 49² = 2401)

  (24, –23): right side offset = 6·24 + (24 – (–23)) = 144 + 47 = 191  
                        → 2401 – 191 = 2210  
  (24, –22): right side offset = 144 + 46 = 190 → 2401 – 190 = 2211  
  (24, –21): right side offset = 144 + 45 = 189 → 2401 – 189 = 2212  

• Ring 22 (k = 22, maxVal = 45² = 2025)

  (22, –22): bottom-right            → 2025  
  (22, –21): right side offset = 6·22 + (22 – (–21)) = 132 + 43 = 175  
                        → 2025 – 175 = 1850  

--------------------------------------------------------------------
4.  Sum of the eight neighbours

2025 + 2027 + 2208 + 2209 + 2210 + 2211 + 2212 + 1850  
= 16 952

--------------------------------------------------------------------
Answer: 16 952
